  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study assess whether a small-group seminar intervention to prevent weight gain is
      effective in a general university student population, and to address the relative role of
      biological vs. lifestyle factors in predicting weight gain in humans.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
